## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing
1. Run `npm run dev` on the project
2. Open `http://localhost:3000` in the browser
3. Verify visually:
   - Navbar shows actual company logo image (not text "T")
   - Hero section has split layout with illustration on right
   - Feature/stats bar shows horizontal icon row
   - Course cards have images, badges, ratings
   - Footer shows actual logo
   - All animations work smoothly
   - Responsive on mobile viewport sizes
4. Click all navigation links to verify they still work
5. Check that no console errors appear

### Content Verification
- Verify all existing text content is preserved (headlines, descriptions, course data, stats)
- Verify all navigation links and routing are unchanged
- Verify auth buttons (Login/Signup) are still present and functional

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a **design-only** change. No routing, auth, CMS, API, or business logic changes. All content stays the same.
